06:40.260 --> 06:49.480
marvelous place called Other. Just some Other place that doesn't have any
reference to where we go in the future. That's the best kind. That's the kind

06:49.480 --> 06:56.160
that I think one of the things that science fiction is for. If you don't like
the government, go ahead and create a new kind of government give it a push and

06:56.160 --> 07:07.700
see how it works uh you can study whole cultures and religions and also some
literature and art i've gone into that in some of my stories which are

07:07.700 --> 07:16.780
essentially in places that occur just other not in the future or in the past
necessarily one of the very finest science fiction books around uh is by

07:16.780 --> 07:27.560
somebody i'm very proud to call one of my ex-students. It's called Wild Seed and
