got into their love, marriage, their sexuality, also into their art, their

21:31.780 --> 21:43.080
literature, their architecture. And so I had a ball with that. Venus Plus X is
not, you know, really a novel at all. It's a tract. It's an exposition of the

21:43.080 --> 21:54.340
ideas that I was getting at the time. Yeah, you wouldn't necessarily advocate
the kind of surgical alteration in that book. No, by no means. You have to be

